27 biennium to be allocated to the Maternal Care Access Grant Program
28 authorized by Section 1.1 of this Part. The Department of Health and Human
29 Services may use up to one percent (1%) of these funds for administrative
30 purposes related to the grant program. The balance of these funds shall be used
